{"blogid": "126656159", "writerAge": "码龄4年", "writerBlogNum": "99", "writerCollect": "56", "writerComment": "10", "writerFan": "54", "writerGrade": "4级", "writerIntegral": "1056", "writerName": "宁然也", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_126656159.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "18713", "writerRankWeekly": "14970", "writerThumb": "23", "writerVisitNum": "71890", "blog_read_count": "384", "blog_time": "已于 2022-09-03 09:43:19 修改", "blog_title": "python生成PDF报告", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-light\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h2><a id=\"_0\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/384170408/answer/2517054828\">如何使用Python制作pdf文档？</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/martin_19/article/details/126504213\">PDF报告生成软件开发（学习记录）</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/ityard/article/details/125139427?ops_request_misc=%257B%2522request%255Fid%2522%253A%2522166208140016781790798447%2522%252C%2522scm%2522%253A%252220140713.130102334..%2522%257D&amp;request_id=166208140016781790798447&amp;biz_id=0&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~baidu_landing_v2~default-3-125139427-null-null.142%5Ev44%5Epc_ran_alice&amp;utm_term=PDF%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90&amp;spm=1018.2226.3001.4187\">Python生成图文并茂的PDF报告</a><br/> <a href=\"https://www.reportlab.com/docs/reportlab-userguide.pdf\">官方用户手册</a></p>\n<h2><a id=\"_7\"></a>字体下载注册问题</h2>\n<p>在windows找到字体文件：C:\\Windows\\Fonts<br/> 在你的python环境引入字体<br/> D:\\devementtool\\Anaconda3-202105\\envs\\pytorchlearn\\Lib\\site-packages\\reportlab\\fonts<br/> 字体一定放在reportlab\\fonts这个文件夹下<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\51bf2254e4d14748a7ef35dda8bddf6b.png\"/></p>\n<p>在python注册字体</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> reportlab\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> reportlab<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pdfbase <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> pdfmetrics  <span class=\"token comment\"># 注册字体</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 注册字体(提前准备好字体文件, 如果同一个文件需要多种字体可以注册多个)</span>\npdfmetrics<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>registerFont<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TTFont<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'SimSun'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'SimSun.ttc'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#宋体</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>SimSun.ttc是字体文件名</p>\n<p>找的途径： style = getSampleStyleSheet()点击getSampleStyleSheet()，在style.py找alignment，找TA_LEFT<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\1e412f90b01447e3bd6ae8a49e4dcfcf.png\"/></p>\n<p>字体对齐方式：<br/> TA_LEFT = 0<br/> TA_CENTER = 1<br/> TA_RIGHT = 2<br/> TA_JUSTIFY = 4</p>\n<pre><code>    'wordWrap':None,        #None means do nothing special\n                            #CJK use Chinese Line breaking\n                            #LTR RTL use left to right / right to left\n                            #with support from pyfribi2 if available\n</code></pre>\n<p>注意事项：<br/> 支持默认的PDF图像类型jpeg，如果安装了Python的PIL扩展，也可以处理其他图像类型</p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "Python", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 1, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-09-03 09:43:19", "summary": "如何使用制作文档？报告生成软件开发学习记录生成图文并茂的报告官方用户手册字体下载注册问题在找到字体文件：在你的环境引入字体字体一定放在这个文件夹下在这里插入图片描述在注册字体注册字体注册字体提前准备好"}